        <p>Suggest a reason why the Central Limit Theorem may not apply with these data.</p>
      </statement>
      <response/>
    </exercise>

    <exercise xml:id="practice-2-9B-b">
      <title>Bootstrap interval for the median</title>
      <statement>
        <p>Create and interpret an informal (<m>\pm</m> 2SE) bootstrap confidence interval for the population median.</p>
      </statement>
      <response/>
    </exercise>
  </subsection>
</section>
